AccountId.description: The client account that's associated with the rule

CurrencyIsoCode.description: If multiple currencies are enabled, this field contains the currency ISO code associated with the record.

EffectiveFromDate.description: The date from when the eligibility rule is active.

EffectiveToDate.description: The date on which the eligibility rule becomes inactive.

EligibilityInitiationType.description: Specifies when the benefit coverage of the employee starts.

EligibilityTerminationType.description: Specifies when the benefit coverage of the employee ends.

EmployeeType.description: Specifies the type of employee the rule applies to.

IsChildEligible.description: Indicates whether the employee's children are eligible for the coverage or not.

IsPartnerEligible.description: Indicates whether the employee's spouse or domestic partner is eligible for the coverage or not.

LastReferencedDate.description: The timestamp when the current user last accessed this record indirectly, for example, through a list view or related record.

LastViewedDate.description: The timestamp when the current user last viewed this record or list view. If this value is null, and LastReferenceDate is not null, the user accessed this record or list view indirectly.
